{
  "stem": "7160.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then after three or four days, we step close to another river.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody was thirsty like hell.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the water was but 100 feet away from us, and we're not allowed to go there to drink water.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anybody goes close, they just shot on the spot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some people got crazy, couldn't take it anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, the thirst makes you crazy, you know, the fever and everything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They shoot quite a few people there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So was somebody I knew from Greece.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was an engineer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he says to us, with the crew people, he says, listen, guys, he says, to my estimation, I think we are so close to the river.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If you guys dig something, you're going to find some water close by here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We don't have to go drink from the water.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I always used to carry a big spoon with me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we start digging with the spoon, and before you know, by that deep, here's water coming down.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a thing of water in the sand and drink it-- whatever, worms, whatever was there, everything tastes good.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there gave us also a little moisture.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So before we-- make the long story short, before we arrive in Germany, there was a train waiting for us, because they don't want the German public to see they was taking so many thousands of people on the road like that, you know?",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And most of them, they were dead-- 3/4 dead, top.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Anybody fall down is shot and in the truck, shot and in the truck.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You have to keep going with the pace, or they threw the dog on top of you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because each German used to have a German Shepherd with him.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
